➜美国公民白宫请愿脱离联邦
https://www.solidot.org/story?sid=32245	42300
在奥巴马重新当选美国总统之后，多达20个州的公民在白宫<a href="https://wwws.whitehouse.gov/petitions">We The People</a>网站请愿要求和平脱离联邦。其中，内布拉斯加州（Nebraska）的<a href="https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/peacefully-grant-state-nebraska-withdraw-united-states-and-create-its-own-new-government/Jf5xVXrS">联署人数</a>已获得超过4千签名（修正错误）；德州<a href="https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/peacefully-grant-state-texas-withdraw-united-states-america-and-create-its-own-new-government/BmdWCP8B">联署人数</a>超过8万；路易斯安那州<a href="https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/peacefully-grant-state-louisiana-withdraw-united-states-america-and-create-its-own-new-government/1wrvtngl">联署人数</a>超过3万。按照规定，如果签名超过2.5万，白宫需要对此<a href="http://www.politico.com/politico44/2012/11/secession-petitions-flood-white-house-website-149291.html">作出回应</a>。